data.description: Discover the perfect blend of space and style in this 3 Bed, 2 Bath home in Pueblo, Colorado. Beyond its charming facade lies a spacious interior featuring a formal dining room, a cozy living room, and a bonus family room for versatile living. Enjoy entertaining on the back deck overlooking the large fenced yard, complete with a convenient storage shed. The upstairs bedroom boasts a fireplace for added warmth and ambiance. With extra parking and a quick drive to I-25, this home seamlessly combines comfort and convenience. Please note the home has leased solar panels. Payoff to be negotiated.
